CMD_BASSBOOST_OPTION_ENABLED: Whether or not bass boost will be enabled. If not specified, it will be toggled.
CMD_BIND_DESCRIPTION: Change the text channel used by Quaver to send messages automatically.
CMD_BIND_OPTION_CHANNEL: The text channel to bind to.

CMD_INFO_DETAIL:
Open-source music bot for small communities.
Source code available [here](https://go.zptx.icu/Quaver), invite [here](%1).
Running version `%2`.
CMD_LOCALE_DESCRIPTION: Change Quaver's locale in this server.
CMD_MOVE_DESCRIPTION: Move a track within the queue.
CMD_MOVE_OPTION_OLDPOSITION: The position of the track to move.
CMD_MOVE_OPTION_NEWPOSITION: The new position to move the track to.
CMD_MOVE_INSUFFICIENT: There aren't enough tracks in the queue to perform a move.
CMD_MOVE_NOT_IN_RANGE: One (or both) of your arguments are out of range.
CMD_MOVE_EQUAL: Your arguments cannot be the same.
CMD_NIGHTCORE_DESCRIPTION: Nightcore mode speeds up your music.
CMD_NIGHTCORE_OPTION_ENABLED: Whether or not nightcore will be enabled. If not specified, it will be toggled.
CMD_PLAY_OPTION_QUERY: What to search for. Links from Spotify, YouTube and more are supported. Searches YouTube by default.
CMD_PLAY_OPTION_INSERT: Whether or not to play the track next.
CMD_PLAY_SPOTIFY_NO_RESULTS: Found no results from your Spotify query.
CMD_REMOVE_DESCRIPTION: Remove a track from the queue.
CMD_REMOVE_OPTION_POSITION: The position of the track to remove.
CMD_REMOVE_EMPTY: There are no tracks in the queue to remove.
CMD_SEARCH_USE_PLAY_CMD: Try using the play command instead.
CMD_SHUFFLE_INSUFFICIENT: There aren't enough tracks in the queue to perform a shuffle.
CMD_SKIP_VOTED: You have already voted to skip this track.
CMD_STOP_DESCRIPTION: Stop the current track and clear the queue.
CMD_STOP_SUCCESS: Stopped the current track and cleared the queue successfully.
CMD_VOLUME_OPTION_NEWVOLUME: The new volume to adjust to.
CMD_VOLUME_NOT_IN_RANGE: That is not within the valid range of `0%` to `200%`.
